StarFlier::

She looked up at the dragon in amazement. "WHoah. I didn't think 
there were other bots here at all. LEt alone one like me. Your boss? 
So there are other bots here?"  The excitement of being with other 
bots filled her emotion chips.  She had been alone for so 
long. "Well, my ship got turned to scrap by a comit, or meteors. 
Something. Anyway, your a dragon huh? That is so wonderful. My name 
is StarFlier. What's your's?"
